description: This was the first time I have talked to a florist. It was only a part-time job but still a pretty weird one for a boy. Besides his peculiar occupation, he was a standard case. The boy wanted a new TV and wasn´t able to pay installments. He was 10 000 behind and needed another 10 000 to pay off the debt. When you sell flowers four hours a day, it´s not easy to erase your debts. He wanted to be debt free, who wouldn´t? 20 000 in total, no problem for me. I offered him my help and he accepted. In fact, he decided really quickly. If only everyone was that reasonable. Maybe the young pervert liked it, he even came all over his hands. Too bad he didn´t have any flowers in his flat, I would put one up his ass. But my cock worked as well :-)
title: Debt Dandy 176
